9. Palindrome Number
discriminate. 
Solution: take out each logit of x, and put it into a new 'copy' from the lower logit. Finally, check if this two equal.

13. Roman to Integer
At first, count all the numbers, then detect if there is reversed pairs, then delete twice of the first character number.

